        <h3
          class="mb-4"
          style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem); font-weight: 700; color: hsl(107 76% 26%); line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: -0.01em;"
        >
          Xbox Gamertag Ideas by Interest or Theme
        </h3>

        <p
          class="mb-4"
          style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 17px); line-height: 1.8; color: #374151;"
        >
          Another strong way to choose a gamertag is to build it around the games, themes, or interests you already enjoy.
        </p>

        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2" style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
          <li style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 17px); line-height: 1.8; color: #374151;">
            <strong style="color: #111827;">Anime-inspired Xbox gamertags:</strong> Great for players who want names shaped by favorite series, characters, or styles.
          </li>
          <li style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 17px); line-height: 1.8; color: #374151;">
            <strong style="color: #111827;">Fantasy and mythology gamertags:</strong> Good for names that feel powerful, dramatic, or story-driven.
          </li>
          <li style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 17px); line-height: 1.8; color: #374151;">
            <strong style="color: #111827;">FPS, RPG, and genre-based gamertags:</strong> Useful if you want the name to match your playstyle.
          </li>
          <li style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 17px); line-height: 1.8; color: #374151;">
            <strong style="color: #111827;">Personality-based gamertags:</strong> Names inspired by how you act, play, or want to be remembered.
          </li>
          <li style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 17px); line-height: 1.8; color: #374151;">
            <strong style="color: #111827;">Sports-themed Xbox gamertags:</strong> A strong option for players who mainly play football, basketball, racing, or other sports titles.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p
          class="mb-6"
          style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 17px); line-height: 1.8; color: #374151;"
        >
          A theme-based name often feels more personal and easier to keep long term because it connects to something you already care about.
        </p>

        <p
          class="mb-6"
          style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 17px); line-height: 1.8; color: #374151;"
        >
          Once you know the style, identity, or theme you want, the generator becomes much more effective. You are no longer just picking random names. You are choosing an Xbox gamertag that fits your personality, your games, and the way you want to be remembered online.
        </p>

        <!-- Ad Banner bottom -->
        <div
